window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Ski Lodge owner Kayla Wolff is dating former Army Ranger Nate Grayson, but she still feels guilty about a former relationship gone wrong. What if dating Nate leads her down the same path as before?</p> <p>Nate is now a private investigator in the wolf pack-run Silver Town, where he's settling in and doing a great job. He wants to give Kayla time to sort out her feelings. He knows she's under a lot of stress taking over more of the management of the lodge because both her brothers' mates are having twins.</p> <p>Nate has had to take over more of the workload at the PI agency himself while his own sister is on maternity leave, so he does his best to be a shoulder for Kayla to lean on. But when his investigation into an abandoned safe and set of keys at the lodge turns a dangerous corner, Kayla and Nate are certain that there's no other wolf they'd rather be with.</p>"; 
